description:
I followed the whispers until I reached them, finally saw them, they were all alive but not live, as if they were buried under a pile of rocks and dirt and bones, only a few parts of them were visible, most of them had different heads. , Each have a different personality
For example, this one seems to be a person who can not keep his mouth shut, he looks like a spy, a beadle maybe, I call him a beadle
Each of these works as a ticket to enter the BULLMASKE party on opensea and FND
And of course, after having 77 tickets, you will receive a complete painting work in Opensea as a gift
Bullmaske Collection has
77 pieces of work on Hic et nunc (each will have 1 or 7 or 11 Edition)
also 77 single painting work on Opensea and 11 Motion painting on Foundation
